    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools used for burnishing or polishing that are made of bone, ivory, smooth wood, or in modern contexts, plastic. Examples of usage include the smoothing and burnishing of paper or leather.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
